<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Materi 5 – Cerita atau Laporan | Kelas 3 SD-CQ</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka+One&family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--green:#27ae60;--gl:#2ecc71;--gd:#1a8a46;--yel:#f1c40f;--ora:#e67e22;--blu:#2980b9;--pin:#e91e8c;--pur:#8e44ad;--red:#e74c3c;--tea:#00b894;--bg:#f0fdf4;--sh:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);--rad:20px}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:#2d3436;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:radial-gradient(circle at 15% 20%,rgba(39,174,96,.08) 0%,transparent 40%),radial-gradient(circle at 85% 80%,rgba(241,196,15,.1) 0%,transparent 40%);pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
/* HEADER */
header{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gd) 0%,var(--green) 60%,var(--tea) 100%);position:relative;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(27,122,55,.3)}
header::after{content:'🌿🌱🦋🌻🐛🌿🌱🦋🌻🐛';position:absolute;bottom:6px;left:0;right:0;text-align:center;font-size:14px;opacity:.35;letter-spacing:4px}
.hdr{max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:22px 20px 30px;text-align:center;position:relative;z-index:1}
.badge-s{display:inline-block;background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);color:#fff;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 12px;border-radius:20px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:7px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3)}
header h1{font-family:'Fredoka One',cursive;font-size:clamp(26px,6vw,42px);color:#fff;line-height:1.15;text-shadow:2px 3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.15)}
header p{color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);font-size:14px;margin-top:5px;font-weight:600}
/* NAV */
.tnw{max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 16px;position:relative;z-index:10}
.tnav{display:flex;gap:3px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.7);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);border-radius:18px 18px 0 0;padding:7px 7px 0;box-shadow:0 -2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08);overflow-x:auto}
.tbtn{flex:1;min-width:90px;padding:9px 8px 13px;border:none;cursor:pointer;background:transparent;font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:12px;color:#888;border-radius:13px 13px 0 0;transition:all .25s;white-space:nowrap}
.tbtn .ti{font-size:17px;display:block;margin-bottom:2px}
.tbtn:hover{color:var(--green);background:rgba(39,174,96,.08)}
.tbtn.active{background:#fff;color:var(--gd);box-shadow:0 -3px 0 var(--green) inset}
/* CONTENT */
.cw{max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 16px 60px;position:relative;z-index:5}
.tp{display:none;background:#fff;border-radius:0 0 var(--rad) var(--rad);box-shadow:var(--sh);padding:26px;animation:fu .35s ease}
.tp.active{display:block}
@keyframes fu{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
/* PERTEMUAN HEADER */
.ph{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:13px;border-radius:15px;padding:15px 18px;margin-bottom:22px;color:#fff}
.ph.p1{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--green),var(--tea))}
.ph.p2{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--blu),var(--pur))}
.pnum{font-family:'Fredoka One';font-size:38px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.22);border-radius:11px;width:56px;height:56px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
.ph h2{font-size:17px;font-weight:800}
.ph p{font-size:13px;opacity:.9;margin-top:2px}
/* STEP CARDS */
.sl{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:11px}
.sc{border:2px solid #e8f5e9;border-radius:15px;overflow:hidden;transition:box-shadow .2s;cursor:pointer}
.sc:hover{box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(39,174,96,.18)}
.sh{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;padding:13px 16px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#f0fdf4,#fff);user-select:none}
.sn{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--green),var(--tea));color:#fff;font-family:'Fredoka One';font-size:17px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
.st{font-weight:800;font-size:14px;color:var(--gd);flex:1}
.stag{font-size:10px;padding:2px 9px;border-radius:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px}
.tm{background:#e3f9ee;color:var(--gd)}.tl{background:#fff3cd;color:#7d5a00}.tt{background:#e8f0fe;color:#1a4fba}
.sa{font-size:17px;transition:transform .25s;color:var(--green)}
.sc.open .sa{transform:rotate(90deg)}
.sb{display:none;padding:16px 18px 18px;border-top:2px dashed #d4edda;background:#fafffe;animation:fu .25s ease}
.sc.open .sb{display:block}
/* BADGES & BOXES */
.mb{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#667eea,#764ba2);color:#fff;padding:5px 13px;border-radius:18px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:11px}
.ib{border-radius:13px;padding:14px 16px;margin:11px 0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7}
.ib.g{background:#e8f8ef;border-left:4px solid var(--green)}
.ib.b{background:#e8f4ff;border-left:4px solid var(--blu)}
.ib.o{background:#fff3e8;border-left:4px solid var(--ora)}
.ib.pk{background:#fff0f7;border-left:4px solid var(--pin)}
.ib.pu{background:#f3e8ff;border-left:4px solid var(--pur)}
.ib.y{background:#fffde7;border-left:4px solid var(--yel)}
.ib h4{font-weight:800;margin-bottom:6px;font-size:14px}
/* STORY CARD */
.strc{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f0fff4,#e8f8ff);border:2px solid #b7e4c7;border-radius:15px;padding:16px 18px;margin:9px 0}
.strc h4{font-family:'Fredoka One';font-size:17px;color:var(--gd);text-align:center;margin-bottom:10px}
.strc p{font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#444}
/* COMPARE TABLE */
.ctb{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;border-radius:11px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.08);margin:10px 0}
.ctb th{padding:11px 13px;font-weight:800;font-size:13px}
.ctb th:first-child{background:#667eea;color:#fff}
.ctb th:nth-child(2){background:var(--green);color:#fff}
.ctb th:nth-child(3){background:var(--ora);color:#fff}
.ctb td{padding:9px 13px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;vertical-align:top;font-size:13px}
.ctb tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}
.ctb tr:nth-child(odd) td{background:#fafafa}
.ctb td:first-child{font-weight:700;color:#555}
/* LAPORAN TEMPLATE */
.lt{background:#fffde7;border:2px dashed #f1c40f;border-radius:15px;padding:16px 18px;margin:9px 0}
.lt h4{font-family:'Fredoka One';color:#7d5a00;font-size:16px;text-align:center;margin-bottom:12px}
.lr{display:flex;gap:7px;margin-bottom:9px;font-size:13px}
.ll{font-weight:800;color:var(--gd);min-width:115px;padding-top:2px;flex-shrink:0}
.lv{color:#555;line-height:1.6}
/* STEP ITEMS */
.si{list-style:none}
.si li{display:flex;gap:11px;align-items:flex-start;padding:9px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px}
.si li:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.sc2{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--green),var(--tea));color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:13px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
/* VOCAB */
.vg{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:9px;margin:9px 0}
.vc{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gl),var(--tea));border-radius:11px;padding:11px 13px;text-align:center;color:#fff;box-shadow:0 3px 10px rgba(39,174,96,.25)}
.vc strong{display:block;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:3px}
.vc span{font-size:11px;opacity:.9;line-height:1.4}
/* OBS TABLE */
.ot{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;border-radius:11px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}
.ot th{background:var(--green);color:#fff;padding:11px;text-align:center;font-weight:800;font-size:13px}
.ot td{padding:9px 11px;border-bottom:1px solid #e8f5e9;text-align:center;font-size:13px}
.ot td:first-child{font-weight:700;color:#555}
.ob{display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:9px;font-weight:700;font-size:11px}
.ob.or{background:#d4edda;color:#1a5c2a}.ob.an{background:#ffeaa7;color:#7d5a00}
/* ===== REVIEW ===== */
.rh{text-align:center;padding:14px 0 22px}
.rh h2{font-family:'Fredoka One';font-size:26px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--blu),var(--pur));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text}
.rh p{color:#666;font-size:14px;margin-top:5px}
.cg{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:13px;margin:14px 0}
.cc{border-radius:15px;padding:15px;text-align:center}
.cc.fk{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e8f5e9,#c8e6c9);border:2px solid var(--green)}
.cc.op{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff3e0,#ffe0b2);border:2px solid var(--ora)}
.cc .ci{font-size:30px;margin-bottom:7px}
.cc h3{font-family:'Fredoka One';font-size:18px;margin-bottom:7px}
.cc.fk h3{color:var(--gd)}.cc.op h3{color:var(--ora)}
.cc ul{list-style:none;font-size:12px;text-align:left}
.cc ul li{padding:2px 0}
.cc.fk ul li::before{content:'✓ ';font-weight:700;color:var(--gd)}
.cc.op ul li::before{content:'✓ ';font-weight:700;color:var(--ora)}
.kb{display:inline-block;margin:2px;padding:2px 9px;border-radius:18px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700}
.ko{background:#ffe0b2;color:var(--ora)}.kf{background:#c8e6c9;color:var(--gd)}
/* REVIEW GAME */
.rp{display:flex;gap:5px;margin-bottom:16px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.rd{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;background:#e8f5e9;border:2px solid #b7e4c7;font-weight:800;font-size:11px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all .3s;color:#888}
.rd.correct{background:var(--green);color:#fff;border-color:var(--gd)}
.rd.wrong{background:var(--red);color:#fff;border-color:#c0392b}
.rd.cur{border-color:var(--blu);color:var(--blu);transform:scale(1.15)}
.rqc{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8f9fa,#fff);border:2px solid #e9ecef;border-radius:17px;padding:20px;text-align:center;margin-bottom:14px}
.rqn{font-size:11px;color:#888;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:9px}
.rqt{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.5;color:#2d3436}
.rbg{display:flex;gap:11px;justify-content:center}
.rb{flex:1;max-width:150px;padding:13px 9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;border-radius:13px;font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:14px;transition:all .2s;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.1)}
.rb.fbtn{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--green),var(--gl));color:#fff}
.rb.obtn{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ora),#f39c12);color:#fff}
.rb:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.15)}
.rb:disabled{transform:none;opacity:.7;cursor:not-allowed}
.rb.ca{box-shadow:0 0 0 3px #27ae60,0 4px 12px rgba(39,174,96,.3)}
.rb.wa{box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--red),0 4px 12px rgba(231,76,60,.3)}
.rfb{text-align:center;padding:11px;border-radius:11px;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin-top:11px;display:none}
.rfb.correct{background:#e8f8ef;color:var(--gd)}.rfb.wrong{background:#fdecea;color:var(--red)}
.rsc{display:none;text-align:center;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#667eea,#764ba2);border-radius:18px;padding:28px;color:#fff}
.rsc h3{font-family:'Fredoka One';font-size:24px;margin-bottom:7px}
.rsb{font-family:'Fredoka One';font-size:60px;line-height:1;margin:11px 0}
.rsc p{font-size:15px;opacity:.9}
.btr{margin-top:14px;padding:11px 26px;background:#fff;color:#667eea;border:none;border-radius:28px;font-family:'Nunito';font-weight:800;font-size:14px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.15)}
.btr:hover{transform:scale(1.05)}
/* ===== MAIN GAME ===== */
.gd{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f3460 0%,#16213e 40%,#1a1a2e 100%);border-radius:18px;padding:26px 22px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:18px}
.gd::before{content:'⭐✨💫🌟⭐✨💫🌟⭐✨';position:absolute;top:7px;left:0;right:0;font-size:11px;opacity:.25;letter-spacing:3px}
.gd h2{font-family:'Fredoka One';font-size:26px;color:#ffd700;text-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(255,215,0,.5);margin-bottom:5px}
.gd p{color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);font-size:13px}
.gs{display:flex;gap:11px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:14px}
.gch{background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);border-radius:18px;padding:5px 13px;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:12px}
.gch span{color:#ffd700}
.tw{position:relative;width:74px;height:74px;margin:0 auto 14px}
.tr{transform:rotate(-90deg)}
.trb{fill:none;stroke:rgba(255,255,255,.15);stroke-width:6}
.trp{fill:none;stroke-width:6;stroke-linecap:round;stroke:#ffd700;transition:stroke-dashoffset 1s linear,stroke .3s}
.tn{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);font-family:'Fredoka One';font-size:22px;color:#fff}
.qc{background:#fff;border-radius:18px;padding:22px;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.1);margin-bottom:14px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.qc::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:4px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--green),var(--blu),var(--pin))}
.qm{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:13px}
.qnb{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--green),var(--tea));color:#fff;padding:3px 11px;border-radius:18px;font-weight:800;font-size:12px}
.qcat{font-size:11px;color:#999;font-weight:700;background:#f5f5f5;padding:2px 9px;border-radius:9px}
.qt{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.6;color:#2d3436;text-align:center;padding:7px 0}
.og{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:9px;margin-top:14px}
.ob2{padding:13px 9px;border:2px solid #e8e8e8;background:#fff;border-radius:13px;font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;color:#444;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;text-align:center;line-height:1.4}
.ob2:hover:not(:disabled){border-color:var(--green);background:#f0fdf4;transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(39,174,96,.2)}
.ob2.correct{background:var(--green);color:#fff;border-color:var(--gd)}
.ob2.wrong{background:var(--red);color:#fff;border-color:#c0392b}
.ob2:disabled{cursor:not-allowed}
.pt{background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:9px;height:7px;margin-bottom:14px;overflow:hidden}
.pf{height:100%;border-radius:9px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--green),var(--tea));transition:width .4s ease}
/* FEEDBACK OVERLAY */
.fo{position:fixed;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(0);border-radius:18px;padding:22px 30px;text-align:center;z-index:1000;transition:transform .25s cubic-bezier(.68,-.55,.265,1.55);min-width:180px}
.fo.show{transform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1)}
.fe{font-size:48px;margin-bottom:7px}
.ft{color:#fff;font-family:'Fredoka One';font-size:22px}
.fs{color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);font-size:13px;margin-top:3px}
/* RESULT */
.res{display:none;text-align:center;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1a2e,#16213e,#0f3460);border-radius:18px;padding:32px 22px;color:#fff}
.res.show{display:block;animation:fu .5s ease}
.rtit{font-family:'Fredoka One';font-size:30px;color:#ffd700;text-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(255,215,0,.5);margin-bottom:7px}
.rsco{font-family:'Fredoka One';font-size:72px;color:#ffd700;line-height:1;margin:14px 0;text-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(255,215,0,.6)}
.rstr{font-size:34px;margin:11px 0;letter-spacing:3px}
.rdt{display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:14px 0}
.rcp{background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25);border-radius:18px;padding:7px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;color:#fff}
.rcp b{color:#ffd700}
.rmsg{background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:13px;padding:13px;margin:14px 0;font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.9);font-weight:600}
.bpa{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ffd700,#f39c12);color:#1a1a2e;border:none;border-radius:28px;padding:13px 32px;font-family:'Nunito';font-weight:800;font-size:15px;cursor:pointer;margin:7px;transition:all .2s;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(255,215,0,.4)}
.bpa:hover{transform:scale(1.05)}
.fwk{font-size:26px;margin:7px 0;animation:bnc .5s ease infinite alternate}
@keyframes bnc{from{transform:translateY(0)}to{transform:translateY(-7px)}}
/* START SCREEN */
.ss{text-align:center;padding:18px 8px}
.ss .be{font-size:68px;animation:bnc 1s ease infinite alternate}
.ss h2{font-family:'Fredoka One';font-size:26px;color:#ffd700;margin:11px 0 5px}
.ss p{color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);font-size:14px;margin-bottom:7px}
.gr{background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:13px;padding:14px;margin:14px auto;max-width:340px;text-align:left}
.gr li{color:rgba(255,255,255,.9);font-size:13px;padding:4px 0;list-style:none}
.gr li::before{content:'⚡ '}
.bst{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ffd700,#f39c12);color:#1a1a2e;border:none;border-radius:28px;padding:14px 44px;font-family:'Nunito';font-weight:800;font-size:17px;cursor:pointer;margin-top:9px;transition:all .2s;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(255,215,0,.4);animation:pb 1.5s ease infinite}
@keyframes pb{0%,100%{transform:scale(1)}50%{transform:scale(1.05)}}
.bst:hover{transform:scale(1.08)!important}
/* CONFETTI */
.cc2{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:999;overflow:hidden}
.cp{position:absolute;animation:cff 2.5s linear forwards;border-radius:2px}
@keyframes cff{0%{transform:translateY(-100px) rotate(0deg);opacity:1}100%{transform:translateY(100vh) rotate(720deg);opacity:0}}
/* RESPONSIVE */
@media(max-width:600px){.tp{padding:16px 12px}.cg{grid-template-columns:1fr}.og{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.qt{font-size:13px}.ob2{font-size:12px;padding:11px 7px}.lr{flex-direction:column;gap:2px}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="hdr">
    <div class="badge-s">📖 SD Islam Tahfizh Cahaya Qur'an | Kelas 3 Semester II TA. 2025/26</div>
    <h1>🌿 MATERI 5<br>Cerita atau Laporan</h1>
    <p>Bahasa Indonesia • Klik setiap judul untuk membuka materi</p>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="tnw">
  <div class="tnav">
    <button class="tbtn active" onclick="swT('p1')"><span class="ti">📅</span>Pertemuan 1</button>
    <button class="tbtn" onclick="swT('p2')"><span class="ti">📅</span>Pertemuan 2</button>
    <button class="tbtn" onclick="swT('rv')"><span class="ti">🔍</span>Review Fakta/Opini</button>
    <button class="tbtn" onclick="swT('gm')"><span class="ti">🎮</span>Games 30 Soal</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="cw">

<!-- ======== PERTEMUAN 1 ======== -->
<div id="p1" class="tp active">
  <div class="ph p1"><div class="pnum">1</div><div><h2>Pertemuan Pertama</h2><p>Membaca cerita, memahami laporan, belajar perbedaan cerita & laporan</p></div></div>
  <div class="ib y" style="margin-bottom:16px">💡 <strong>Petunjuk:</strong> Klik setiap nomor/judul untuk membuka materinya. Kerjakan secara urut ya! 😊</div>
  <div class="sl">

    <div class="sc" onclick="tog(this)">
      <div class="sh"><div class="sn">1</div><div class="st">📖 Membaca Cerita "Memilah Sampah di Sekolah"</div><span class="stag tm">MATERI</span><span class="sa">▶</span></div>
      <div class="sb">
        <div class="mb">📘 Modul Halaman 45</div>
        <div class="ib y">Buka modulmu di halaman 45 dan bacalah cerita di bawah ini dengan saksama! 👀</div>
        <div class="strc">
          <h4>Memilah Sampah di Sekolah</h4>
          <p>Hari Jumat pagi, guru mengajak kami belajar memilah sampah di halaman sekolah. Di sana ada tiga tempat sampah berwarna hijau, kuning, dan biru. Tempat sampah hijau untuk sampah organik, kuning untuk sampah anorganik, dan biru untuk sampah kertas.</p><br>
